                    <span>This is the WORST book I have used in my study of finance.  It is full of errors and it is written in such a way that it is extremely hard to understand for an average student.  There are lots of calculations that are unexplained, assumtions are made that are never addressed,and it is just plain vague in virtually all subjects it discusses.  Buy  a different title if you actually want to learn about finance.</span>
                  
              
